  "body": {
    "export_view": {
      "value": "<p>Released 04/12/17 9:49PM CT</p><h2 id=\"id-1.12.4-InternalPurchaseOrders(transfers)\">Internal Purchase Orders (transfers)</h2><ul><li><p>Internal transfers are now fully disabled if only one location is active</p></li><li><p>Inactive locations no longer show in the internal supplier list</p></li><li><p>Inventory managers can now print packing slips</p></li><li><p>Added a &quot;view serials&quot; interface to view serial numbers for inventory transferred</p></li></ul><h2 id=\"id-1.12.4-CatalogItemLabels\">Catalog Item Labels</h2><p>Display location override price on catalog item labels.</p><h2 id=\"id-1.12.4-ReconcileallcreditcardsonVCT\">Reconcile all credit cards on VCT</h2><p>Fixed and enhanced the feature that allows non-integrated credit cards to be reconciled on a single VCT.</p><h2 id=\"id-1.12.4-InactiveItemTypes\">Inactive Item Types</h2><p>Exclude catalog items from searches and list views where the parent Item Type is inactive.</p><h2 id=\"id-1.12.4-MaxDiscountAllowedforManagerRole\">Max Discount Allowed for Manager Role</h2><p>The manager role\u00a0now\u00a0no longer grants\u00a0the ability to grant\u00a0100% discount on tickets, unless no max discount is defined on their staff profile. An admin\u00a0can set the max discount that a\u00a0manager may\u00a0grant with the \u00a0&quot;max discount&quot; field, and it will be enforced as it is enforced with other user roles.</p><h2 id=\"id-1.12.4-NewLoadingIndicator\">New Loading Indicator</h2><p>We added a new loading indicator for your viewing pleasure.</p><h2 id=\"id-1.12.4-InvoiceFilters\">Invoice\u00a0Filters</h2><p>The &quot;customer&quot; and &quot;billing agent&quot; filters on the invoice screen\u00a0were not filtering as intended. These filters have been updated, and they will filter results with a stricter logic.</p><h2 id=\"id-1.12.4-BrandedLogosonEmailReceipts\">Branded\u00a0Logos on Email Receipts</h2><p>Some of you have had trouble getting logos to show up for emailed receipts and invoices.\u00a0We ironed out some wrinkles related to uploaded images on receipts &amp; invoices which should resolve any lingering issues here.</p><h2 id=\"id-1.12.4-PAXPaymentDuplicates\">PAX Payment Duplicates</h2><p>We fixed a\u00a0rare case where payments would be saved twice to the ticket after processing.</p>",
      "representation": "export_view",
